subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Iben Tinning of Denmark shot a five-under-par 67 to take a one-shot lead after three rounds of the Dubai Ladies Masters, the season-ending tournament on the Ladies European Tour. She was at nine-under 207 entering Sunday’s final round, with Annika Sorenstam, Laura Davies and Veronica Zorzi at 208.
